Product information

Pros and cons

According to our freezer expert

  • With the ice twister, you always have ice cubes within reach for a glass of soda.
  • You save up to 250 on energy costs over the lifespan thanks to the C energy label.
  • You can freeze a large amount of groceries in one go thanks to the 336L freezer space.
  • It's not possible to place this upright freezer in a shed, garage, or pantry that's colder than 10C.

Description

You can make ice cubes in no time with the ice twister of the Siemens GS58NAWCV. To do this, fill the tray with drinking water and pull the lever. That's useful for in your cola or your cocktail. Thanks to the C energy label, this upright freezer is very energy-efficient. This means you pay less in energy costs. With a 336L net capacity, you have room for 7 to 10 full shopping bags of frozen fruit, bread, and snacks. Thanks to the air circulation, it doesn't matter where you place your food. It's equally cold everywhere. Thanks to No Frost, the upright freezer stays free of ice and you don't have to defrost it. On the inside of the door, there are 2 cooling elements that hold the cold better. You can put them in your cooler on a warm day.

Tips for using this product

  • Ice twister

Insure your freezer

Receive more coverage in case of damage than with your standard warranty. Coolblue takes care of everything: from taking out the insurance to repairs. Is a repair not possible? You receive the purchase price as CoolblueCredit.

What am I insured for?

  • Fall and impact damage
  • Water damage
  • Manufacturing defects outside the warranty

What am I not insured for?

  • Damage you deliberately cause
  • Damage that doesn't affect the product functioning (such as scratches)
  • Damage due to gross negligence

XCover insurace

XCover is allowed to arrange and process insurances on behalf of the insurer. The insurances are governed by Belgium law. If you have a complaint, you can contact the or our customer service .

Read more about insurance

How do I insure my freezer?

First, add your freezer to your shopping cart. On the next page, choose the Protection Plan below. You always have a 30-day return window and pay no deductible in case of damage.

XCover Protection without theft cover
  • 5-year advance payment
    90,- one-time payment (18,- per year)
  • 4-year advance payment
    65,- one-time payment (16,25 per year)

The insurance can be canceled every year, even if you have paid in advance. If you cancel earlier, you will receive a refund for the overpaid amount.
